Package org.sakaiproject.tool.section.jsf.backingbean

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SectionEditor
    Backing beans that are used to modify (add or edit) sections should implement SectionEditor.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddSectionsBean
    Controls the add sections page.
    ConfigurationBean  
    CourseBean
    Provides the current course uuid for a given user session.
    CourseDependentBean
    Base class for all JSF backing beans relying on knowledge of the current course context.
    EditManagersBean
    Controls the edit managers page (where TAs are assigned to sections).
    EditSectionBean
    Controls the edit and delete sections pages.
    EditStudentsBean
    Controls the edit students page (where students are assigned to sections).
    EditStudentSectionsBean
    Controls the edit student sections page (where a single student is assigned to sections).

    InitializableBean

    OptionsBean

    OverviewBean
    Controls the overview page.
    PreferencesBean
    Stores user preferences for table sorting and paging.
    RosterBean
    Controls the roster page.
    StudentViewBean
